elems.code:
{
  
  all u : User | u not in u.suggested

  
  all u, y : User | y in u.follows implies y not in u.suggested

  
  all u, x : User | 
    (x in u.suggested) iff 
    (some y : User | y in u.follows and x in y.follows and x not in u.follows and u != x)
}

{
    all u : User |
        no (u.suggested & u.follows) and
   		u not in u.suggested and
  		all s : u.suggested |
            some f : u.follows | s in f.follows
}

{
	
		all u : User, v : User | 
		v in u.suggested implies 
		(not v in u.follows) and
		(some f : User | f in u.follows and v in f.follows) and
		u != v
}

{
  all u1, u2, u3: User | 
    (u2 in u1.follows and          
     u3 in u2.follows and          
     u3 !in u1.follows and         
     u1 != u3)                     
    implies u3 in u1.suggested     
}

{
	// Suggested are other users followed by followed users, but not yet followed.
all u :User | 
  all uf:User | 
    all us:User |
  	  (u!=uf and uf!=us and
        
        uf in u.follows and 
        us in uf.follows and 
        us not in u.follows)
  
  	   => us in u.suggested
  
  
	
}

{
    all u: User, u2: User |
        u != u2 and
        u2 not in u.follows and
        (some u3: u.follows | u2 in u3.follows) implies
        u2 not in u.suggested
}

{
  all u1, u2, u3: User | 
    (u2 in u1.follows and          
     u3 in u2.follows and          
     u3 !in u1.follows and         
     u1 != u3)                     
    implies u3 = u1.suggested     
}

{
    
    all u1, u2 : User | 
        all u3 : User | 
  			(u1 != u2 and u1 != u3 and u2 != u3) implies (
            (u3 in u2.suggested) implies 
            (u2 in u1.follows and u3 in u2.follows and (not u3 in u1.follows)))
}

{
	// Suggested are other users followed by followed users, but not yet followed.
  	all u1,u2,u3 : User | 
  		u1 != u2 and u1 != u3 and u2 != u3 and
  		u1 not in Influencer and
  		u2 not in Influencer and
  		u3 not in Influencer and
  		u3 in u2.follows and 
  		u2 in u1.follows 
  		implies u3 in suggested.u1
	
}

{
    
    all u1: User | 
        all u2: User | 
            (u1 in follows.u2) implies 
                (some u3: User | 
                    (u2 in follows.u3) and 
                    not (u3 in follows.u1) and 
                    u3 != u1 and 
                    u3 in u1.suggested)
}
